    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于此游戏</h2>     《下班模拟器》是一款密室逃脱类型的游戏。在游戏里面，你将扮演一个受公司压榨，深夜里还在带病疲劳加班的程序员，带病上夜班的感觉如此难受，而公司老板却为了尽快项目上线盈利，竟然想办法关闭了所有的出口，逼你今晚必须搞定所有的问题才能下班。你实在无法忍受，决定无论如何也要尽快想办法回家休息，你需要探索这个办公室，找寻物品并用手里的东西解开一些谜题并最终开门回家或是&quot;搞定&quot;所有问题。一定要小心老板和保安，假装在工作让他们走开，或是灵巧走位，在没椅子的桌子下面或者在大衣柜里藏身，或是干脆找到&quot;武器&quot;把他们打晕！总之别让他们抓住，被抓住了就没啥好果子，因为他们“凶狠异常”并且缺乏人性！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特性</h2>*   <i>紧张有趣的追逐体验</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/d6b916235df63f6594cfdd7ffd78e075.poster.avif?t=1667924252\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/d6b916235df63f6594cfdd7ffd78e075.webm?t=1667924252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/d6b916235df63f6594cfdd7ffd78e075.mp4?t=1667924252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>*   <i>灵巧走位避免被抓</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/cdb273adfbbbbb1e8845879be1ebc2ef.poster.avif?t=1667924252\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/cdb273adfbbbbb1e8845879be1ebc2ef.webm?t=1667924252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/cdb273adfbbbbb1e8845879be1ebc2ef.mp4?t=1667924252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>*   <i>丰富的道具，有意思的谜题</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/d5d777a9cd0a0ae1a8e20bdcdd950044.poster.avif?t=1667924252\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/d5d777a9cd0a0ae1a8e20bdcdd950044.webm?t=1667924252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/d5d777a9cd0a0ae1a8e20bdcdd950044.mp4?t=1667924252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>*   <i>少见的职场环境</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/0d7b7b497b6d9c3395681e80c9de1a8f.poster.avif?t=1667924252\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/0d7b7b497b6d9c3395681e80c9de1a8f.webm?t=1667924252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/0d7b7b497b6d9c3395681e80c9de1a8f.mp4?t=1667924252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>*   <i>气愤难忍，暴力通关</i><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/8fc2855e790191acc133338f389f49f4.poster.avif?t=1667924252\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/8fc2855e790191acc133338f389f49f4.webm?t=1667924252\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/8fc2855e790191acc133338f389f49f4.mp4?t=1667924252\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/f7880d1d5c6d9cef2a49607f5b3218ae.poster.avif?t=1667924252\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1728430/extras/f7